text: The Tempest is the tenth studio album by American horrorcore band, Insane Clown Posse. It was released on March 20, 2007. The producer of the album was Mike E. Clark. ==Track listing== ==Reception== The album peaked at number 20 on the Billboard 200, peaked number 1 on the Top Independent Albums and peaked at number 20 on the Top Internet Albums.Artist Search for "insane clown posse" | AllMusic ==References== Category:2007 albums Category:Insane Clown Posse albums Category:Concept albums
